      <title>莫迪在邦民意调查中获胜有望提振印度资金流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/modi-s-win-in-state-polls-seen-boosting-case-for-india-inflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场参与者表示，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党在关键州选举中获胜可能会增强印度对外国投资者的吸引力，并导致更多资金流入当地股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/modi-s-win-in-state-polls-seen-boosting-case-for-india-inflows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 01:34:35 GMT</pubDate>
