    <item>
      <title>日本央行政策押注引发的动荡震动了日本信贷市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/turbulence-from-boj-policy-bets-shakes-up-japan-credit-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于成本保持相对较低且稳定，多年来的超低利率为日元债券市场的借款人创造了令人羡慕的地位。现在，有关日本央行最终将收紧政策的猜测让市场面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/turbulence-from-boj-policy-bets-shakes-up-japan-credit-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:59:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价随美国利率稳定，委内瑞拉供应成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场猜测美联储已经结束加息以及美国可能再次收紧对委内瑞拉供应的制裁，油价在连续六周下跌后企稳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:52:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鸽派言论推动现货黄金上涨至创纪录水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/spot-gold-rises-to-record-2-091-73-ounce-on-dovish-fed-remarks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美联储试图缓和乐观情绪，但由于人们对美国明年初降息的预期不断增强，金价突破了疫情期间创下的历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/spot-gold-rises-to-record-2-091-73-ounce-on-dovish-fed-remarks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:18:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金创历史新高，比特币在美联储削减押注的情况下攀升：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/asian-stocks-to-rise-after-us-shrugs-off-powell-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黄金飙升至新纪录，比特币在亚洲交易中突破 40,000 美元，市场对美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔关于政策制定者并不急于放松利率的提醒不以为然。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/asian-stocks-to-rise-after-us-shrugs-off-powell-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 22:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚央行行长表示令吉将复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-01/malaysia-s-ringgit-to-recover-central-bank-chief-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚国家银行行长阿卜杜勒·拉希德·加福尔表示，一旦发达经济体央行完成加息，他预计令吉将与其他新兴市场货币一起复苏。他在迪拜举行的 COP28 峰会间隙接受彭博社的 Yousef Gamal El-Din 采访时发表了上述言论。
 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-01/malaysia-s-ringgit-to-recover-central-bank-chief-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 09:07:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
